<br>
Let's say I'm playing from the US, you're playing from Europe, and someone else is playing from Asia.  We all attend a ToV North raid which is worth, say... 2 AP per dragon.  I stay for 9 dragons, getting 18 AP.  You stay for 6 dragons getting 12 AP.  The player from Asia stays for 4 dragons getting 8 AP.  Total AP for me for that raid is 18 AP, total AP for you for that raid is 15 AP, total AP for the other player is 12 AP.  Eurpoean players get an AP modifier of 1.25 and players from Asia get a modifier of 1.50.  This serves to equalize the overall player AP and makes things &quot;fair&quot; for those of us who aren't in the standard time zone.  <br>
<br>
You also have the fact that the officers decide the loot instead of people buying it with points, this is the ultimate equalizer.  The officers know these players are playing from a different country and take that into account.  It's a very, very fair system. <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Having said that, one thing that is pissing me off of late are some dicks in our guild who see dkp as a paycheque and only turn up to raids with sufficient dkp/time ratios. They really need to be ejected.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
That's the great thing about AP.  You don't buy your items, they're rewarded based on overall participation... so people always show up to raids and have fun, vs. worrying about how many points they're going to get for killing uber_mob02. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucassiusruneblaze.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cassius Runeblaze</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>I <3 Zealots</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/28/02 7:08:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12071.topic&index=66>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best item you've seen rot?</span><hr size=1> <br>
